HEADWORD: Blent
<hw>Blent</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> of <er>Blend</er>
to mingle. <def>Mingled; mixed; blended; also, polluted;
stained.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Rider and horse, friend, foe, in one red burial
